webpackJsonp([0xf49f942f854c],{574:function(t,a){t.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>There are 5 actions you can take on a report in your inbox:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add comment</li>\n<li>Close report</li>\n<li>Change state</li>\n<li>Assign report</li>\n<li>Set award</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-8bf13.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 32.73657289002558%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-actions"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-49813.png 125w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/report-actions-1-7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35-8bf13.png 1564w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Add Comment</h3>\n<p>You can dialogue with hackers or team members or make notes about the report through adding comments.</p>\n<p>To add a comment:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Make sure the action picker is set to <strong>Add comment</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select who you would like to make the comment visible to. You can select from these options:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Team only</td>\n<td>Only the members of your program will be able to view the comment.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>All participants</td>\n<td>All participants of the report will be able to view the comment.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em>Note: When you\'re adding a comment to your internal team only, the comment box will turn red.</em></p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-cfafd.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 32.390745501285345%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-actions-2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-49813.png 125w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/report-action-2-31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982-cfafd.png 1556w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Close Report</h3>\n<p>You can close a report to mark that it\'s either:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Resolved</li>\n<li>Informative</li>\n<li>Not Applicable</li>\n<li>Duplicate</li>\n<li>Spam</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To close a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Close report</strong> in the action picker.</li>\n<li>Select the status of the report in the <strong>Select status</strong> action picker.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Close report</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-51938.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 32.94871794871795%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-action-3"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-49813.png 125w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/report-actions-3-00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9-51938.png 1560w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Change State</h3>\n<p>You can change the state of a report to be marked as either <em>triaged</em> or <em>new</em>. This\'ll help you keep track of what state your report is in.</p>\n<p>To change the state of a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Change state</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Select the state of the report. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Triaged</td>\n<td>The report has passed the initial validation and is pending resolution. You can briefly describe the next steps in the comments section such as further investigation, escalation, engineer preparing a fix. *(Optional) When you select triage, you can enter the reference ID to your integration in the \n<strong>Reference ID</strong>\n field.*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>New</td>\n<td>The report is pending triage and validation.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start="4">\n<li>\n<p>When the report is</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Click <strong>Change state</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-cfafd.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 35.2185089974293%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-action-5"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-49813.png 125w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/report-action-5-cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc-cfafd.png 1556w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Assign Report</h3>\n<p>You can assign reports to individual members in your program or to groups to evaluate and take action on the report.</p>\n<p>To assign a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Assign report</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Enter the username of the assignee or the group.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Assign report</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-14e2d.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 34.02328589909444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="assign report"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-49813.png 125w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/assign-report-db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa-14e2d.png 1546w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Set Award</h3>\n<p>You can mark that you\'ve rewarded a hacker with swag or a monetary amount through setting awards.</p>\n<p>To set an award to a hacker for the report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Set award</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Select the type of award you want to reward the hacker with. You can choose from these options:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Amount</td>\n<td>Mark that you\'ve rewarded the hacker with a specific dollar amount for the vulnerability.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>None ( ineligible)</td>\n<td>The report is ineligible for a bounty. It\'s best to explain the reasons to hackers in the comments section, why the report is ineligible.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Suggest amount</td>\n<td>Suggest a bounty amount to award the hacker. Only internal members of your program will be able to view your bounty suggestion.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Swag</td>\n<td>Mark that you\'ve rewarded the hacker with swag.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start="4">\n<li>Click <strong>Set award</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-acf87.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 33.29081632653062%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="report-action-4"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-e7ffa.png"\n        srcset="/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-49813.png 125w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-dc8a5.png 250w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-e7ffa.png 500w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-dda24.png 750w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-c5f18.png 1000w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-22484.png 1500w,\n/static/report-action-4-37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11-acf87.png 1568w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>',frontmatter:{path:"/programs/report-actions.html",id:"programs/report-actions",title:"Report Actions",description:null}}},pathContext:{}}}});
